{{Quote|&mdash;hailing the ''Millennium Falcon''. Repeat, this is the New Republic scout vessel ''Gabrielle'' hailing the ''Millennium Falcon''. Please respond on S-thread six zero niner.|A [[Unidentified communications officer (Gabrielle)|communications officer]]|<ref name="Star By Star">''[[The New Jedi Order: Star by Star]]''</ref>}}
The '''''Gabrielle''''' was supposedly a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] scout vessel inservice in [[27 ABY/Legends|27 ABY]]. It was said to be investigating the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] fleet gathering in the [[Black Bantha Nebula/Legends|Black Bantha Nebula]]. In reality, it was a code used by [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]], signaling a meeting between himself and [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]]. At the meeting, Solo turned over a great amount of information on the Vong fleet.

